    metaDescription: "Essential guide to soakaway installation in Hampshire. Covers building regulations, percolation tests, soil types, and planning permission.",
    excerpt: "Planning to install a soakaway in Hampshire? Understand the UK Building Regulations, soil testing requirements, and whether a soakaway is suitable for your property.",
